Subject: 11-17 Second Ave, Blacktown -Mechanical - Fee proposal


Good day. 
We would like to invite you the tendering process for the Construction Documentation for 11-17 Second Ave, Blacktown. 

Please allow for the following in your quote 
-	Design compliance declaration for CC.
-	Design certificate for CC.
-	Liaison During Construction Phase
-	Specifications 
-	Specifications declaration 
-	CFD modelling report. 
-	Occupation Certificate 

Project description 
-	5 Levels of Basements
-	324 Residential apartments

Please find link below following documents and attached SOW for your reference: 

Blacktown 

We really appreciate your time and assistance. Please submit fee proposal by COB Friday 15th of March or earlier if possible.

Note: after your fee proposal is received, we will arrange for a “meet and greet” meeting

Regards

Donnie Joardar
Pre-Construction Project Coordinator

The project is a residential develop and consists of:

-      Level 1 to level 20, with Residential Apartments, approximately 339 apartments.
